missionSettings.description:
Welcome to City Dogfight! An accessible, PVP, fast paced team deathmatch mode at the heart of the city. 
Rules for an enjoyable game:
1) Don't camp airbases. Let players get airborne first before attacking.
2) Don't target factories, platforms, helipads and aircraft shelters on purpose.

Aircraft carriers can be used to resupply or refuel.
Each faction also has two separate, heavily guarded resupply platforms built in the water.
At 2025 points one nuke is available, at which point the gamemode switches to an Apocalyptic Dogfight!

Rules for an enjoyable game: 
1. Don't camp the spawn points. Let players get airborne first.
2. Don't target helipads, factories or aircraft shelters on purpose.

Welcome to City Dogfight! An accessible, PVP, fast paced team deathmatch mode at the heart of the city. 
Rules for an enjoyable game: 
1) Don't camp airbases. Let players get airborne first before attacking. 
2) Don't target factories, platforms, helipads and aircraft shelters on purpose.
Aircraft carriers can be used to resupply or refuel.
Each faction has two resupply platforms on land, and two separate, heavily guarded resupply platforms built in the water.

At 2025 points one nuke is available, at which point the game mode switches to an Apocalyptic Dogfight!
If the main spawn points of each faction are destroyed, new spawn points will appear.
